    FlowAjaxTiles3View

    public class AjaxTiles3View
extends org.springframework.web.servlet.view.tiles3.TilesView
    Tiles 3 view implementation that is able to handle partial rendering for Spring Javascript Ajax requests.

    This implementation uses the DefaultAjaxHandler by default to determine whether the current request is an Ajax request. On an Ajax request, a "fragments" parameter will be extracted from the request in order to determine which attributes to render from the current tiles view.

    Since:
    2.4
    Author:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
